column16: Jeremy Hazelbaker triples (1) on a ground ball to right fielder Hunter Renfroe.   Nick Ahmed scores.    Daniel Descalso scores.

Nick Ahmed reaches on a missed catch error by first baseman Hector Sanchez, assist to third baseman Ryan Schimpf.
Brandon Drury pops out to shortstop Erick Aybar.
Emilio Bonifacio grounds into a double play, second baseman Yangervis Solarte to shortstop Erick Aybar to first baseman Wil Myers.   Johan Camargo out at 2nd.
Johan Camargo singles on a ground ball to center fielder Manuel Margot.   Brandon Phillips scores.    Anthony Recker to 3rd.
Anthony Recker singles on a sharp line drive to left fielder Travis Jankowski.   Brandon Phillips to 2nd.
Adonis Garcia pops out to third baseman Ryan Schimpf in foul territory.
Andrew Toles walks.   Yasiel Puig scores.    Austin Barnes to 3rd.    Scott Van Slyke to 2nd.
Scott Van Slyke walks.   Yasiel Puig to 3rd.    Austin Barnes to 2nd.
Chase Utley grounds out, third baseman Ryan Schimpf to first baseman Wil Myers.
Justin Turner singles on a ground ball to left fielder Travis Jankowski, deflected by shortstop Erick Aybar.
Corey Seager homers (1) on a line drive to center field.   Yasiel Puig scores.    Clayton Kershaw scores.
Andrew Toles pops out to third baseman Ryan Schimpf on the infield fly rule.
Yasiel Puig doubles (1) on a sharp line drive to left fielder Travis Jankowski.
Yasmani Grandal lines out sharply to left fielder Travis Jankowski.
Joc Pederson flies out sharply to left fielder Travis Jankowski.
Logan Forsythe flies out to right fielder Hunter Renfroe.
